===========================================================================
$NetBSD$

Append the following line to your .emacs file:

  (autoload 'vimrc-mode "vimrc-mode"
            "Major mode for editing `.vimrc', `xxx.vim' and `.exrc' files." t)
  (add-to-list 'auto-mode-alist '("\\.vim\\(rc\\)?$" . vimrc-mode))

